<refsect1 id="harfbuzz-hb-glib.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>Functions for using HarfBuzz with the GLib library.</para>
<para>HarfBuzz supports using GLib to provide Unicode data, by attaching
GLib functions to the virtual methods in a <link linkend="hb-unicode-funcs-t"><type>hb_unicode_funcs_t</type></link> function
structure.</para>

</refsect1>
