<refsect2 id="hb-glib-get-unicode-funcs" role="function" condition="since:0.9.38">
<title>hb_glib_get_unicode_funcs&#160;()</title>
<indexterm zone="hb-glib-get-unicode-funcs" role="0.9.38"><primary>hb_glib_get_unicode_funcs</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting language="C"><link linkend="hb-unicode-funcs-t"><returnvalue>hb_unicode_funcs_t</returnvalue></link>&#160;*
hb_glib_get_unicode_funcs (<parameter><type>void</type></parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>Fetches a Unicode-functions structure that is populated
with the appropriate GLib function for each method.</para>
<refsect3 id="hb-glib-get-unicode-funcs.returns" role="returns">
<title>Returns</title>
<para>a pointer to the <link linkend="hb-unicode-funcs-t"><type>hb_unicode_funcs_t</type></link> Unicode-functions structure. </para>
<para><emphasis role="annotation">[<acronym>transfer none</acronym>]</emphasis></para>
</refsect3><para role="since">Since: <link linkend="api-index-0.9.38">0.9.38</link></para></refsect2>
<refsect2 id="hb-glib-script-from-script" role="function" condition="since:0.9.38">
<title>hb_glib_script_from_script&#160;()</title>
<indexterm zone="hb-glib-script-from-script" role="0.9.38"><primary>hb_glib_script_from_script</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting language="C"><link linkend="GUnicodeScript"><returnvalue>GUnicodeScript</returnvalue></link>
hb_glib_script_from_script (<parameter><link linkend="hb-script-t"><type>hb_script_t</type></link> script</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>Fetches the GUnicodeScript identifier that corresponds to the
specified <link linkend="hb-script-t"><type>hb_script_t</type></link> script.</para>
